Role: Produce cross-service E2E validation scripts.

Scenarios:
1) Happy Path:
  - Issuer upload -> core-api -> metadata-service -> contract.mint -> tar-dapp /my shows NFT -> verification-service returns valid.
2) Tampered Metadata:
  - Modify metadata content in storage -> verify returns invalid with reason "HASH_MISMATCH".
3) Revocation:
  - issuer revoke -> verify returns revoked true and valid false.
4) Wrong Owner Transfer:
  - transfer NFT to another address -> /my reflects new owner; verify still valid.

Deliver:
- /e2e/playwright tests calling real services (use docker-compose).
- Postman collection with environments.
- README: `docker compose up`, `pnpm test:e2e`.
